Add 1 Tb lemon juice, 1 tsp cumin, 2 Tb olive oil, 1/4 C. Parsley and you are there. Great way to increase your iron and get your veggies in!

Rating: 4
I like to use what is in season in my own garden so I used fresh peas and my own lemon, parsley and green onion. It was a beautiful way to make the most of my garden. The cumin is the perfect touch.

