I used canned peas, added more onion & lemon juice and it was great! I will be making this again!

Rating: 3
I've made this a few times and found it was better with good quality frozen peas. The fresh peas weren't tasty enough for some reason. That's the only change I made. I've served it at a dinner party with other appetizers and had a lot of comments about how good and fresh it tasted. I'm making it again today.

